metadata.author: Disney
metadata.description: When future lion king Simba is born, not everyone in the kingdom celebrates the new cub’s arrival. Simba’s cruel uncle, Scar, has plans of his own that result in tragedy. Exiled from the pride, and with the help of a curious pair of newfound friends, will Simba figure out how to grow up - and take back what is rightfully his?
